OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FStop asking about salary   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fhistory, employers urged   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, UK employers should stop asking        
OL,6, jobseekers about their previous        
OL,7, salaries, a campaign group is urging.  
OL,9,FThe Fawcett Society says asking about  
OL,10,Fprevious pay when recruiting           
OL,11,Fcontributes to the gender pay gap, by  
OL,12,Fkeeping women on lower wages.          
OL,14,FIts survey of 2,200 working adults     
OL,15,Ffound that 47% of people had been asked
OL,16,Fabout past salaries.                   
OL,18,FMeanwhile, 61% of women said the       
OL,19,Fquestion had an impact on their        
OL,20,Fconfidence to negotiate better pay.    
